OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781902064
OL,3,CTeam Wales announce athletes for
OL,4,CGlasgow 2026 Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FTeam Wales have announced the athletes
OL,7,Fwho will represent the nation at the
OL,8,F2026 Glasgow Commonwealth Games,
OL,9,Ftaking place from 23 July to 2 August
OL,10,F2026.
OL,12,F114 athletes will travel to Glasgow
OL,13,Fnext month for the 23rd Commonwealth
OL,14,FGames, where they will compete across
OL,15,Ften sports including athletics, track
OL,16,Fcycling, and swimming.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
