OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781902064
OL,3,CTeam Wales announce athletes for
OL,4,CGlasgow 2026 Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FAmong the hopefuls are some familiar
OL,7,Fnames like sprinter Jeremiah Azu who
OL,8,Fhas previously won gold at the world
OL,9,Fchampionships and took home bronze at
OL,10,Fthe 2024 Paris Olympics.
OL,12,FCarmarthen born Emma Finucane will be
OL,13,Fhoping to emulate her recent success
OL,14,Fwhen she competes in the track cycling
OL,15,Fevents in Glasgow. She won three
OL,16,Fmedals at the 2024 Paris Olympics
OL,17,Fincluding a gold in the team sprint.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
