OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781902064
OL,3,CTeam Wales announce athletes for
OL,4,CGlasgow 2026 Commonwealth Games
OL,6,F19 year old Ruby Evans will be
OL,7,Frepresenting Wales when she takes part
OL,8,Fin gymnastics next month. Last year
OL,9,Fshe come home with a silver medal at
OL,10,Fthe world championships in Jakarta.
OL,12,FDouble olympic gold medalist Matthew
OL,13,FRichards MBE will be one of the medal
OL,14,Ffavourites for the Welsh swim team. He
OL,15,Fwill be hoping for success in the pool
OL,16,Fin his second commonwealth games.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
