OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781902064
OL,3,CTeam Wales announce athletes for
OL,4,CGlasgow 2026 Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FOf the 114 athletes selected, 22 are
OL,7,Fpara-athletes. Unlike the olympics and
OL,8,Fparalympics, the para events will run
OL,9,Fat the same time as the non-para
OL,10,Fevents.
OL,12,FSome of those hoping for success in
OL,13,FGlasgow include Bridgend born field
OL,14,Fathlete Aled Davies OBE. The five-time
OL,15,Fparalympic medalist will make his
OL,16,Fthird appearance at a commonwealth
OL,17,Fgames.
OL,19,FThe two-time paralympic medalist
OL,20,FOlivia Breen has also been selected as
OL,21,Fpart of the Welsh athletics team.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
