PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781902064
OL,3,CTeam Wales announce athletes for
OL,4,CGlasgow 2026 Commonwealth Games
OL,6,F2024 Paralympic gold medalist James
OL,7,FBall will be hoping to repeat his
OL,8,Fsuccess when he races round the Sir
OL,9,FChris Hoy velodrome in the track
OL,10,Fcycling events.
OL,12,FTeam Wales will be led by Chef de
OL,13,FMission Gethin Jones who said; "It is
OL,14,Fan incredible honour to lead Team
OL,15,FWales this summer in Glasgow and to
OL,16,Fserve as spokesperson for this
OL,17,Ftalented group of athletes."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
