OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1781902064
OL,3,CTeam Wales announce athletes for
OL,4,CGlasgow 2026 Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FHe added: "This group represents the
OL,7,Fvery best of Welsh sport`dedicated,
OL,8,Fambitious and proud to wear the red
OL,9,Fjersey. We are building on the legacy
OL,10,Fof 2014 with real belief, and I
OL,11,Fcouldn't be prouder to be part of this
OL,12,Fteam.
OL,14,F"I can't wait to see what they achieve
OL,15,Fin Glasgow."
OL,17,FThe full list of team Wales competing
OL,18,Fat the 2026 Glasgow Commonwealth Games.
OL,20,FTrack Cycling
